properties.NAME: Ivey Gulledge Road
properties.DESC: ADT on Ivey Gulledge From Old Cartersville to Seven Hills is 3950, the segment from Seven HIlls to Frey Road is 2440
properties.JUST: This roadway has a lower ADT and is better suited as minor collector classification. Projected growth along the corridor has decreased over the last few years.

properties.NAME: Dabbs Bridge Road
properties.DESC: The ADT on this segment of Dabbs Bridge Road is 4900
properties.JUST: The roadway has a lower traffic count, and the traffic has been decreasing over the years.  The majority of Dabbs Bridge Road is already classified as a Minor Collector.

properties.NAME: Hiram-Douglasville Highway (SR 92)
properties.DESC: Through this segment of SR 92 counts were taken as high as 18340 in 2012 at US 278 counter 0174.  SR 92 carries a large amount of traffic trying to get to I-20 in Douglasville, I-75 in Cobb County or Trucks trying to get to the intermodal yard in Austell
properties.JUST: All of SR 92 is under design to be widened and reconstructed.  A portion of this segment is going from a 2 lane to a 6 lane roadway.  All other legs are going from a 2 lane to a 4 lane roadway with a divided median.  The majority of the trips entering and leaving Paulding County are either along US 278 or SR 92.

properties.NAME: Rosedale Drive
properties.DESC: Rosedale Drive has 3 ADT's.  From Cobb Line to Cleburne Pkwy is 1880, Cleburne Pkwy to Seaboard Ave is 4860, Seaboard Ave to SR 92 is 3470
properties.JUST: Traffic counts are lower on this roadway and characteristics meet more of a minor collector.

properties.NAME: Harmony Grove Church Road
properties.DESC: Current ADT on Harmony Grove Church Road is 5750
properties.JUST: Conforming to the surrounding network.  A good portion of Harmony Grove Church Road is already a Minor Collector.
